Package: rpsi
Type: Package
Title: Inference using the Population Stability Index
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Ed", family = "Peyton", email = "edppeyton@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1427-0306")))
Maintainer: Ed Peyton <edppeyton@gmail.com>
Description: Calculation of the population stability index (commonly used in
  credit risk) and the evaluation of meaningful thresholds for inferring stability.
  Based on "Statistical properties of the population stability index", Yurdakul & Naranjo (2020) <doi:10.21314/JRMV.2020.227>.
